%h1 Start an Instance of the Image

%p
  With the image pushed to your provider account, you can start instances
  when desired.

%p
  We will take you through starting an instance of the image using Aeolus's
  web interface.  Then, if you are using Amazon EC2, we will show you how to connect to that image remotely using
  SSH.

